# 🧠 AI Prompt Optimization Guide
### From Vague → Precise → Production-Quality Output
> Version 2.0 · Built during 100 Days of AI Hustle · Day 2
> Updated: Added Few-Shot Prompting + Chain of Thought sections

---

## ⚡ QUICK REFERENCE — The 4-Layer Framework

```
LAYER 1 → ROLE     "You are a [specific expert]..."
LAYER 2 → CONTEXT  "Here is the situation / codebase / constraints..."
LAYER 3 → TASK     "Your specific job is to [numbered asks]..."
LAYER 4 → FORMAT   "Return your answer as [exact structure]..."
```

> **Golden Rule:**
> Vague prompt = AI decides what matters.
> Specific prompt = YOU decide what matters.

