## 💥 COMBINING BOTH — FEW-SHOT + CHAIN OF THOUGHT

This is the most powerful combination.
Use it for your most important, high-stakes prompts.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  FEW-SHOT tells the AI:                                │
│  "This is what perfect output looks like"              │
│                                                         │
│  CHAIN OF THOUGHT tells the AI:                        │
│  "This is how to THINK before producing it"            │
│                                                         │
│  COMBINED:                                             │
│  AI knows both the destination AND the route           │
│  = Most consistent, highest quality output possible    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

