## 🎯 WHICH TECHNIQUE TO USE WHEN

```
┌──────────────────────┬────────────────┬────────────────────┐
│ SITUATION            │ TECHNIQUE      │ REASON             │
├──────────────────────┼────────────────┼────────────────────┤
│ Need consistent      │ FEW-SHOT       │ AI matches your    │
│ format every time    │                │ example exactly    │
├──────────────────────┼────────────────┼────────────────────┤
│ Complex logic or     │ CHAIN OF       │ Forces planning    │
│ multi-step reasoning │ THOUGHT        │ before output      │
├──────────────────────┼────────────────┼────────────────────┤
│ High quality output  │ BOTH COMBINED  │ Best of both —     │
│ that must be perfect │                │ quality + thinking │
├──────────────────────┼────────────────┼────────────────────┤
│ Simple factual       │ NEITHER        │ Overhead not       │
│ questions            │                │ needed             │
├──────────────────────┼────────────────┼────────────────────┤
│ Creative brainstorm  │ CHAIN OF       │ Explore angles     │
│                      │ THOUGHT only   │ before committing  │
└──────────────────────┴────────────────┴────────────────────┘
```

