## 🔥 THE 60-SECOND PAUSE

Before hitting send on ANY prompt:

```
✅ ROLE:     Specific expert? Not just "AI assistant"?
✅ CONTEXT:  Stack? Team? Constraints? Priority order?
✅ CoT:      Should I force step-by-step thinking first?
✅ FEW-SHOT: Do I have an example of perfect output?
✅ TASK:     Numbered and specific? Not open-ended?
✅ FORMAT:   Exact structure specified? Table? Code block?

If ANY is NO → fix before sending.
```

